org.apache.poi.util

Class CommonsLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.util.CommonsLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    POILogger 

    public class CommonsLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements POILogger
    An implementation of the POILogger using the Apache Commons Logging framework. Which itself can be configured to send log to various different log frameworks and even allows to create a small wrapper for custom log frameworks.(${t_0ed87a686fb74976bfcc62eb629e264b})
